Finance.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The course aims to improve the learner's knowledge of financial English covering the most important financial terminology. The course materials, exercises and self tests help students to practice the vocabulary independently.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student:
1) knows and uses the basic financial terminology in English;
2) finds, analyses and assesses critically professional texts;
3) understand the content of the financial readings or listening tasks, and can complete assignments based on them;
4) understands the content heard and can answer questions.
